## Chinese Gun4ir TC4 Style Gun ##
# This gun has a trigger and 4 side buttons x3 on the left x1 on the right #
# When using this gun on TC4 Namco 256 edit this map add TEST, UP and A buttons so you can calibrate gun in test menu #
# After Gun calibration set map buttons back to previous settings #

BTN_TRIGGER CONTROLLER_TRIGGER
BTN_TOP2 CONTROLLER_COIN
BTN_PINKIE CONTROLLER_A
BTN_THUMB CONTROLLER_B
BTN_THUMB2 CONTROLLER_C

ABS_X CONTROLLER_ANALOGUE_X REVERSED
ABS_Y CONTROLLER_ANALOGUE_Y
